title: Kylie Jenner Wishes Tyga a Happy Birthday With Series of Topless and Other Sultry Snaps
text:
Kylie Jenner Wishes Tyga a Happy Birthday With Series of Topless and Other Sultry Snaps By James Devaney/GC Images 
Kylie Jenner has given Tyga quite the 27th birthday to remember. 
The 20-year-old Keeping Up With the Kardashians star posted on her Instagram page two professionally shot photos of the two embracing while she is topless. She also shared a series of sultry videos on Snapchat showing her lip-syncing and singing the ultra-NSFW R&B song "Woosah" by Jeremih , Juicy J & Twista with a friend. 
"Happy birthday baby," she wrote on Instagram. Photos A video posted by Kylie Jenner Snapchats (@kylizzlesnapchats) on Nov 19, 2016 at 7:26am PST 
Two of her Snapchat posts also contained a caption that read, "Happy birthday Tyga" with caricatures of her and the rapper, with her sporting her platinum blonde hair and a slinky white plunging jumpsuit. Snapchat / Kylie Jenner Nov 18, 2016 at 11:11pm PST Snapchat / Tyga Snapchat / Tyga 
Tyga is not seen in Kylie's Snapchat posts. However, on Saturday, he posted on his Snapchat a selfie showing him wearing a New York Mets cap and using the same "Happy Birthday Tyga" message and graphics, as well as a sweet photo of him wearing the same outfit while posing with his girlfriend Friday at a gathering with friends. 
The two celebrated his birthday early. Kylie and the rapper's 4-year-old son King Cairo threw him a surprise birthday celebration Thursday. 
Watch the season finale of Keeping Up With the Kardashians Sunday, Nov. 20 at 9 p.m., only on E!
